frameDefinitions: A Winner has victory over an Loser.
An Agent or a Cause disperses or scatters Individuals from the Source,a relatively confined space, to a the Goal_area, a broader space.
An Entity (generally food) is exposed to a Heat_source whose Temperature may also be specified.
Due to chemical, nuclear, or other reactions, an Explosive explodes, potentially causing damage to the surrounding area.
This frame contains nouns denoting a rank or level within an established hierarchy.
A Location is characterized by a high amount of (often goal-oriented)
frameExamples: She <t>scattered</t> his ashes in the bay.
Bacon was <t>frying</t> in the pan, and a great heap of eggs already lay steaming on a plate.
The bomb <t>exploded</t> in the middle of the plaza.
listRoleDefinitions: The individual or individuals who beat the <fen>Loser</fen>.
The individual or individuals that get beat by the <fen>Winner</fen>.
When the <fen>Winner</fen> has victory over the <fen>Loser</fen>.
The location where the <fen>Winner</fen> has victory <fen>Loser</fen>.

An event or force that causes that <fen>Individuals</fen> to disperse.
The <fen>Time</fen> when the <fen>Individuals</fen> are dispersed.
The <fen>Place</fen> where the dispersing event happens.
The <fen>Entity</fen> (often a food item)  that absorbs heat.
The <fen>Container</fen> that holds the <fen>Entity</fen> that absorbs the heat.

The <fen>Time</fen> when the heat absorption takes place.

The <fen>Location</fen> where a lot of activity is taking place, or prototypically takes place.

The <fen>Individuals</fen> are engaged in the <fen>Activity</fen>, creating a lively <fen>Location</fen>.
The <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Location</fen> is characterized by a lot of activity.
The larger or general area where the <fen>Location</fen> is lively.
